description: Episode 3: Rich Twink, Poor Twink In San Francisco, class and wealth have never kept anyone apart. Take boyfriends Blake (Marcus Mojo) and Jake (Jake Lyons). Blake was born with a silver spoon in his mouth, while Jake's more accustomed to washing spoons at his job in a restaurant. And when Blake gets the big inheritance that he's been waiting for, he decides it's time to show Jake some of the finer things in life.
series: Golden Gate Season 02 - The Perfect Ten
title: Golden Gate Season 02 - The Perfect Ten
